      "latestNote": "SEM training was completed on 1 July. The ion-milled sample was mounted with carbon tape and aluminium tape, carbon-coated five times to about 125 Angstrom, and observed by SEM-EDS.",
      "stageNote": "Conductive mounting and carbon coating prepared the ion-milled Orgueil CI1 section for initial SE/BSE imaging and EDS reconnaissance.",
