    "bodyHtml": "<p class=\"mission-entry-kicker\">SOL 001 / 2026-04-01</p>\n            <h3>Mission Log 001 · Graduation research plan established</h3>\n            <p>\n              I began my graduation research project, “Cosmomineralogical Study of Dolomite in the Orgueil CI1 Chondrite:\n              Aqueous Alteration Processes and Material Evolution in a Primitive Asteroidal Parent Body.” The project asks how dolomite\n              in the Orgueil CI1 chondrite records aqueous alteration processes and material evolution in a primitive asteroidal parent body,\n              and how its occurrence relates to clay-rich regions.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              The initial plan is to investigate dolomite occurrence, morphology, chemical composition, and crystallographic\n              features using SEM/EPMA, single-grain XRD, and TEM observations across micro- to nanometre scales.\n            </p>\n            <div class=\"log-tags\">\n              <span>Graduation Research</span>\n              <span>Orgueil</span>\n              <span>CI1 Chondrite</span>\n              <span>Dolomite</span>\n              <span>Clay Minerals</span>\n              <span>SEM / EPMA / TEM</span>\n            </div>\n                <a class=\"mission-back-to-index\" href=\"#mission-index\">Back to Mission Index ↑</a>",
    "stageJa": "研究計画の確定",
